# 📖 Chapter 14 – Schema Markup (Structured Data)

---

# 🎯 Chapter Objective

Is chapter me hum Schema Markup (Structured Data) ko detail me samjhenge. Aap seekhenge ki Schema kya hota hai, Google ise kaise use karta hai, Rich Results kya hote hain aur different types ke schema website par kaise implement kiye jate hain.

---

# 14.1 What is Schema Markup?

**Schema Markup** ek structured code format hai jo search engines ko webpage ke content ko better tarike se samajhne me help karta hai.

Simple Words:

> **Schema = Google ko website ki language samjhana.**

Example:

Agar page par ek product hai to schema Google ko batata hai:

* Product Name
* Price
* Brand
* Availability
* Rating

---

# 14.2 Why Schema is Important?

Schema directly ranking guarantee nahi karta.

Lekin:

* Rich Results
* Better Visibility
* Higher CTR
* Better User Experience

provide kar sakta hai.

Benefits:

* Better Search Appearance
* Rich Snippets
* More Clicks
* Better Crawling
* Better Context Understanding

