# 14.4 Types of Schema

Popular Schema Types:

* Organization
* Local Business
* Product
* Article
* FAQ
* Breadcrumb
* Review
* Event
* Video
* Person

Har website ko apni requirement ke according schema use karna chahiye.

---

# 14.5 Organization Schema

Company ki information define karta hai.

Contains:

* Company Name
* Logo
* Website
* Contact
* Social Profiles

Business websites ke liye recommended.

---

# 14.6 Local Business Schema

Local businesses ke liye.

Contains:

* Business Name
* Address
* Phone
* Opening Hours
* Location
* Reviews

SafePro jaise businesses ke liye essential.

---

# 14.7 Product Schema

Product pages ke liye.

Contains:

* Product Name
* Brand
* Price
* Currency
* Availability
* Rating

Product pages ko rich snippets mil sakte hain.

---

# 14.8 Article Schema

Blogs aur articles ke liye.

Contains:

* Title
* Author
* Publish Date
* Modified Date
* Featured Image

Google News aur search results me useful.

---

# 14.9 FAQ Schema

Frequently Asked Questions ko structured format me show karta hai.

Benefits:

* Better User Experience
* Search engines ko content structure samajhne me help

*(Note: Google FAQ rich results ka display apni policies ke hisaab se decide karta hai.)*

---

# 14.10 Breadcrumb Schema

Breadcrumb Navigation ko define karta hai.

Example:

```text id="mxb6tt"
Home

>

Products

>

Fire Extinguisher

>

ABC Fire Extinguisher
```

Benefits:

* Better Navigation
* Better Search Appearance

---

# 14.11 Review Schema

Customer Reviews aur Ratings ko represent karta hai.

Contains:

* Rating
* Reviewer
* Review Text

Reviews genuine hone chahiye.

---

# 14.12 JSON-LD

Google JSON-LD format recommend karta hai.

Benefits:

* Easy Implementation
* Easy Maintenance
* Official Recommendation

Structured data ke liye JSON-LD preferred format hai.

---

# 14.13 Rich Results

Schema implementation ke baad Google kuch pages ko enhanced appearance de sakta hai.

Examples:

* Product Information
* Reviews
* FAQs
* Breadcrumbs
* Organization Details

Rich Results visibility improve karte hain.

---

# 14.14 Schema Validation

Implementation ke baad validation karna zaruri hai.

Useful Tools:

* Google Rich Results Test
* Schema Markup Validator

Errors fix karna important hai.

